"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nzk1665702810152.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nzk1665702810152.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nzk1665702810152.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nzk1665702810152\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Insert Glyph \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Select an image to be loaded into the Repository as a glyph.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__p_d6827e1_d6828e1_d6829e1\">The image you select and its properties are displayed. However, you cannot edit the displayed image or change any of its properties.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__section_stb_cyf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820910e58\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__ul_km5_cyf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3359e1_d3360e1_d3361e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oqd1665702810300.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oqd1665702810300.html\" title=\"The file name of the image to insert.\">Primary File</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3362e1_d3363e1_d3364e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eqw1665702810372.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eqw1665702810372.html\" title=\"The file name of the image to be used as a secondary glyph. The secondary glyph is used as a shadow of the primary glyph.\">Secondary File</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3365e1_d3366e1_d3367e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgl1665702810445.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgl1665702810445.html\" title=\"Specify how the glyph is displayed on the form.\">Display</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__p_d6833e1_d6834e1_d6835e1\">The following properties are derived from the original image\n        and cannot be changed.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__ul_nm5_cyf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3368e1_d3369e1_d3370e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Height</span>—height of the glyph in\n          pixels; read-only. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3371e1_d3372e1_d3373e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Width</span>—width of the glyph in\n          pixels; read-only.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__li_d3374e1_d3375e1_d3376e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Colors</span>—number of colors used in\n          the image; read-only. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__p_d6836e1_d6837e1_d6838e1\">Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so the\n        properties <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI-Specific</span>, and\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Full-Color</span> cannot be modified:</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__section_lcf_dyf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820910e127\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nzk1665702810152__p_d6842e1_d6843e1_d6844e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cpe1705582470714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cpe1705582470714.html\" title=\"Glyphs are maintained and deployed in a runtime library.\">Create and Maintain Glyphs</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421513\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Insert Glyph Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Insert Glyph Select an image to be loaded into the Repository as a glyph. The image you select and its properties are displayed. However, you cannot edit the displayed image or change any of its properties. Properties Primary File Secondary File Display The following properties are derived from the original image and cannot be changed. Height —height of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Width —width of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Colors —number of colors used in the image; read-only. Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so the properties GUI , GUI-Specific , and Full-Color cannot be modified: How to Create and Maintain Glyphs Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}